MASS  -1  OG2D2     15.99940 ! carbonyl O: negative groups: carboxylates, carbonate
MASS  -1  OG2D3     15.99940 ! carbonyl O: ketones
MASS  -1  OG2D4     15.99940 ! 6-mem aromatic carbonyl oxygen (nucleic bases)
